## Mask Class Implementation - Complete (2025-10-28)

Successfully completed the Mask class implementation for handling date/time input constraints with proper value propagation and constraint adaptation.

**Mask Class Overview:**
- Generic `Mask<T>` class representing fixed number of parts with constraints
- Handles value propagation when constraints don't allow direct insertion
- Supports constraint changes with intelligent value adaptation
- Manages content changes with proper deletion/insertion handling

**Key Implementation Details:**

