   - `ChangePart`: Handles value changes with propagation logic
   - `InsertItem`: Respects both AllowedValues and MaxLength constraints
   - `DeleteItem`: Removes items from specific parts
   - `UpdateConstraints`: Adapts existing values to new constraints
   - `ProcessContentChange`: Handles complex content modifications
   - `FindClosestValue`: Maps values to closest allowed values by index
   - `DecideSingleOptions`: Handles single-value constraint scenarios

